<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.5">
<l>iṉivār caṭaiyiṉiṟ kaṅkaiyeṉ pāḷaiyaṅ kattirunta</l>
<l>kaṉivāy malaimaṅkai kāṇileṉ ceytikai yiṟcilaiyāṉ</l>
<l>muṉivār tiripuram mūṉṟumven taṉṟucen tīyilmuḻkat</l>
<l>taṉivār kaṇaiyoṉṟi ṉālmikak kōttaveñ caṅkaraṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Now, if the daughter of the mountain with a fruit mouth who is in [your] body</l>
<l>sees her who is called Gaṅgā in [your] overflowing matted locks, what can you do,</l>
<l>our Śaṅkara who strung much with a single long arrow alone the bow in [your] hand,</l>
<l>so that all three enemy cities burned that day and were sunk in red fire?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
